WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.470
Hey, good morning family. Praise the

00:00:02.480 --> 00:00:04.789
Lord. Thank you for joining me today.

00:00:04.799 --> 00:00:07.749
There is a lot going on again as

00:00:07.759 --> 00:00:09.990
usual, but I just wanted to say

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:13.350
happy Palm Sunday. We have one

00:00:13.360 --> 00:00:15.430
week from today that we are able to

00:00:15.440 --> 00:00:17.710
celebrate the Lord Jesus Christ and his

00:00:17.720 --> 00:00:20.150
resurrection. What a time of the

00:00:20.160 --> 00:00:22.630
year it is! This is my favorite time

00:00:22.640 --> 00:00:24.550
of the year, y'all. I mean, whenever the

00:00:24.560 --> 00:00:27.029
spring is here, the grass is

00:00:27.039 --> 00:00:29.109
coming out, all the beautiful trees

00:00:29.119 --> 00:00:31.750
are budding, and all the birds are

00:00:31.760 --> 00:00:34.310
coming back from the south,

00:00:34.320 --> 00:00:36.229
I personally believe, other than

00:00:36.239 --> 00:00:37.670
fall, it doesn't get better than that. I

00:00:37.680 --> 00:00:41.069
love fall, too; I love the colors. But

00:00:41.079 --> 00:00:43.510
I'm excited about

00:00:43.520 --> 00:00:45.350
resurrection Sunday.

00:00:45.360 --> 00:00:46.790
We're going to pray for the protection

00:00:46.800 --> 00:00:49.190
over the people today for resurrection

00:00:49.200 --> 00:00:52.150
Sunday, that no terrorist attacks, no

00:00:52.160 --> 00:00:54.869
plots, and no plans of the evil one would

00:00:54.879 --> 00:00:57.270
come against us as we go into our houses

00:00:57.280 --> 00:00:59.990
of worship to worship our risen savior.

00:00:59.990 --> 00:01:00.000
I

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:02.069
know that the enemy

00:01:02.079 --> 00:01:03.670
comes to kill, steal, and destroy, but

00:01:03.680 --> 00:01:05.910
we have power and authority over him.

00:01:05.920 --> 00:01:08.390
We're not going to allow, in the name

00:01:08.400 --> 00:01:10.469
of Jesus, any of that to happen in any

00:01:10.479 --> 00:01:12.390
places of the earth. The Lord

00:01:12.400 --> 00:01:14.390
warned us when I've told

00:01:14.400 --> 00:01:16.230
you all about praying

00:01:16.240 --> 00:01:18.070
over the churches in the Middle East,

00:01:18.080 --> 00:01:19.429
our brothers and sisters in the Middle

00:01:19.439 --> 00:01:20.950
East, praying over them that they would

00:01:20.960 --> 00:01:23.670
have safety in this time of worship. And

00:01:23.680 --> 00:01:25.590
even in the United States of

00:01:25.600 --> 00:01:27.789
America, I know

00:01:27.799 --> 00:01:31.749
that we keep things at bay as we

00:01:31.759 --> 00:01:33.990
take our authority, take

00:01:34.000 --> 00:01:36.870
communion, pray daily, and come

00:01:36.880 --> 00:01:39.270
before him boldly, taking our rightful

00:01:39.280 --> 00:01:42.069
place and seat next to him. I know a lot

00:01:42.079 --> 00:01:44.310
of people liked the tithing video. I made

00:01:44.320 --> 00:01:46.389
that; I try to be real with people, but

00:01:46.399 --> 00:01:47.670
you're not going to appease

00:01:47.680 --> 00:01:49.109
everybody. So, I'm just like,

00:01:49.119 --> 00:01:50.550
'Whatever. If you like it, you like it;

00:01:50.550 --> 00:01:50.560
if

00:01:50.560 --> 00:01:52.149
you don't, you don't.'It's what we believe, it's

00:01:52.159 --> 00:01:54.550
how we live, and this is

00:01:54.550 --> 00:01:54.560
how

00:01:54.560 --> 00:01:56.389
I'll continue to live. And what I

00:01:56.399 --> 00:01:58.550
believe is that unless the Holy

00:01:58.560 --> 00:02:00.469
Spirit corrects me, I'm just going to

00:02:00.479 --> 00:02:01.990
keep on keeping on because I've been

00:02:02.000 --> 00:02:03.389
doing it for 20

00:02:03.399 --> 00:02:06.550
years. So, it is what it is.

00:02:06.560 --> 00:02:08.550
People ask me, 'Brandon, what do

00:02:08.560 --> 00:02:10.469
you believe?'So, we just tell you,

00:02:10.479 --> 00:02:11.910
'Hey, this is where

00:02:11.920 --> 00:02:14.150
I'm at.'And if I told you the

00:02:14.150 --> 00:02:14.160
hundredfold

00:02:14.160 --> 00:02:16.070
ground, you'd get ticked off

00:02:16.080 --> 00:02:17.910
and wouldn't watch the channels anymore

00:02:17.910 --> 00:02:17.920
because

00:02:17.920 --> 00:02:19.830
I know some of the people you can't

00:02:19.840 --> 00:02:22.390
stand. So, we don't even

00:02:22.400 --> 00:02:24.470
tell you the hundredfold ground, but I know

00:02:24.480 --> 00:02:26.390
what the hundredfold ground is because I

00:02:26.400 --> 00:02:30.309
studied it. It

00:02:30.319 --> 00:02:31.630
took me

00:02:31.640 --> 00:02:35.910
years of sowing and praying and

00:02:35.920 --> 00:02:38.229
listening to the Holy Spirit and asking

00:02:38.239 --> 00:02:41.509
him what the hundredfold ground is. I

00:02:41.519 --> 00:02:43.910
found some nuggets, but that came

00:02:43.920 --> 00:02:47.350
through a lot of spiritual pressure.

00:02:47.360 --> 00:02:49.910
I try to hint

00:02:49.920 --> 00:02:52.390
around sometimes around these preachers

00:02:52.400 --> 00:02:54.470
that I know the hundredfold ground's

00:02:54.480 --> 00:02:56.869
on, and then I know the ones

00:02:56.869 --> 00:02:56.879
whose

00:02:56.879 --> 00:02:59.270
ground is bad ground. I say it's crap

00:02:59.280 --> 00:03:01.750
ground that doesn't grow anything at all.

00:03:01.760 --> 00:03:04.149
People really follow some of those

00:03:04.159 --> 00:03:05.830
folks and they go, 'Oh yeah, they're

00:03:05.840 --> 00:03:06.949
really good ground.'I say, 'No, that ground

00:03:06.959 --> 00:03:09.030
sucks.'I'm

00:03:09.040 --> 00:03:10.949
just being real. Probably not

00:03:10.959 --> 00:03:13.030
a good word to use, but it's just

00:03:13.040 --> 00:03:15.509
true. And you've got the one ground

00:03:15.519 --> 00:03:17.110
that's really good and they go, 'We

00:03:17.120 --> 00:03:19.270
can't stand them because they have jets and

00:03:19.280 --> 00:03:21.070
they have all this

00:03:21.070 --> 00:03:21.080
stuff.'Folks,

00:03:21.080 --> 00:03:23.710
I'll give you a hint on some

00:03:23.720 --> 00:03:26.830
things: if they are successful in

00:03:26.840 --> 00:03:29.670
ministry, the Bible says if you're

00:03:29.680 --> 00:03:32.390
faithful with little, God will make

00:03:32.400 --> 00:03:36.550
you ruler over much. So, God is

00:03:36.560 --> 00:03:39.430
the God of increase. He's the one that

00:03:39.440 --> 00:03:42.309
brings the increase on folks. And if

00:03:42.319 --> 00:03:44.789
they are walking in abundance, they've

00:03:44.799 --> 00:03:47.430
been faithful with what they have and

00:03:47.440 --> 00:03:50.390
God's giving them more. So if you see

00:03:50.400 --> 00:03:52.470
somebody who doesn't have much and their

00:03:52.480 --> 00:03:54.949
ministry isn't flourishing year after

00:03:54.959 --> 00:03:57.429
year and they're

00:03:57.439 --> 00:03:59.509
staying the same, they haven't passed

00:03:59.519 --> 00:04:02.470
the test. It takes you going from

00:04:02.480 --> 00:04:06.070
glory to glory, and you pass the test,

00:04:06.080 --> 00:04:07.789
and he gives you

00:04:07.799 --> 00:04:11.589
more like the talents. But you get mad

00:04:11.599 --> 00:04:13.750
and want to crucify the guy who has more

00:04:13.760 --> 00:04:15.270
and they go, 'Well, how much do they

00:04:15.280 --> 00:04:16.550
have? They have too much; they

00:04:16.560 --> 00:04:19.069
must have swindled it out of an old

00:04:19.069 --> 00:04:19.079
lady.'Folks,

00:04:19.079 --> 00:04:22.550
come on. God is the God of

00:04:22.560 --> 00:04:25.189
increase. So,

00:04:25.199 --> 00:04:29.990
you want to gravitate to the ground. If

00:04:30.000 --> 00:04:31.749
they've been in

00:04:31.749 --> 00:04:31.759
ministry—not

00:04:31.759 --> 00:04:33.110
like me, I've been in ministry for

00:04:33.120 --> 00:04:35.430
a year and a half going on

00:04:35.440 --> 00:04:37.270
two years. Two years, right? Wow, time

00:04:37.280 --> 00:04:41.110
goes fast. So I'm just a baby in this,

00:04:41.120 --> 00:04:43.110
just like a toddler. But if you've

00:04:43.120 --> 00:04:45.590
been in ministry for 30 years and you're

00:04:45.600 --> 00:04:47.430
still the same and you haven't changed

00:04:47.440 --> 00:04:49.510
and nothing's going from glory to glory

00:04:49.520 --> 00:04:51.990
and your capacity hasn't

00:04:52.000 --> 00:04:54.469
increased to be able to handle

00:04:54.469 --> 00:04:54.479
or

00:04:54.479 --> 00:04:57.270
reach more, you haven't passed the test.

00:04:57.280 --> 00:04:59.430
It doesn't make you bad; it just

00:04:59.430 --> 00:04:59.440
means

00:04:59.440 --> 00:05:02.390
you need to

00:05:02.400 --> 00:05:04.230
go through the refiner's fire so that

00:05:04.240 --> 00:05:06.230
you're able to handle more. Does that

00:05:06.240 --> 00:05:07.430
make sense, what I'm trying to tell you

00:05:07.440 --> 00:05:09.990
all? You see a lot of ministries

00:05:10.000 --> 00:05:11.990
that don't have any more anointing. They

00:05:12.000 --> 00:05:13.510
don't have any more presence. They don't

00:05:13.520 --> 00:05:15.430
have any more stuff going on for them.

00:05:15.440 --> 00:05:17.350
They keep going on

00:05:17.360 --> 00:05:18.710
the same way, going

00:05:18.720 --> 00:05:20.390
around the same mountain all the time.

00:05:20.400 --> 00:05:22.070
You look at them and then

00:05:22.080 --> 00:05:23.950
you give to their ground and you go,

00:05:23.960 --> 00:05:27.590
'Oh, well, I understand.'But then you

00:05:27.590 --> 00:05:27.600
sow

00:05:27.600 --> 00:05:30.310
to the good ground that is blessed

00:05:30.320 --> 00:05:31.510
and you go, 'Wow,'and you

00:05:31.520 --> 00:05:33.830
instantaneously get a big harvest back.

00:05:33.840 --> 00:05:38.310
And I've learned to test the soil.

00:05:38.320 --> 00:05:41.029
I flow that way. I

00:05:41.039 --> 00:05:42.950
tell my wife all the time, 'Let's

00:05:42.950 --> 00:05:42.960
not

00:05:42.960 --> 00:05:45.150
go and give a whole bucket load of

00:05:45.160 --> 00:05:47.310
seed. Let's take

00:05:47.320 --> 00:05:51.830
$100 or $50 and sow it into that ground

00:05:51.840 --> 00:05:53.749
and see how long it takes.'And we'll

00:05:53.759 --> 00:05:56.950
call that in. It's not all on

00:05:56.960 --> 00:05:59.189
the minister, too. By the way, the Holy

00:05:59.199 --> 00:06:00.870
Spirit said this to me:

00:06:00.880 --> 00:06:03.830
'Brandon, you're

00:06:03.840 --> 00:06:05.670
blaming the harvest

00:06:05.680 --> 00:06:08.070
solely on the minister, but the

00:06:08.070 --> 00:06:08.080
sower

00:06:08.080 --> 00:06:11.590
has part of it,

00:06:11.590 --> 00:06:11.600
too.'It's

00:06:11.600 --> 00:06:13.670
not all on the person in the

00:06:13.680 --> 00:06:15.990
soil; it's on the seed

00:06:15.990 --> 00:06:16.000
sower.

00:06:16.000 --> 00:06:18.309
So

00:06:18.319 --> 00:06:20.150
you need to know it's a

00:06:20.150 --> 00:06:20.160
half-and-half

00:06:20.160 --> 00:06:22.870
responsibility.

00:06:22.880 --> 00:06:25.590
You have to name your seed, you have to

00:06:25.600 --> 00:06:27.830
water your seed by watering it with the

00:06:27.840 --> 00:06:30.070
word, calling those things that be not

00:06:30.080 --> 00:06:32.150
as though they were, keeping

00:06:32.150 --> 00:06:32.160
strife

00:06:32.160 --> 00:06:35.110
out of your house, taking communion

00:06:35.120 --> 00:06:37.830
on a day-to-day basis, and sending your

00:06:37.840 --> 00:06:39.990
angels forth in the name of Jesus to

00:06:40.000 --> 00:06:42.230
bring forth your harvest. And if

00:06:42.230 --> 00:06:42.240
you're

00:06:42.240 --> 00:06:45.189
sitting there just idly by going, 'Well,

00:06:45.199 --> 00:06:48.230
I'm just waiting for my good

00:06:48.240 --> 00:06:50.710
truck to come in with all my goods on

00:06:50.720 --> 00:06:55.270
it. Where's my miracle

00:06:55.270 --> 00:06:55.280
package?'I

00:06:55.280 --> 00:06:58.550
told you the Bible says whatever you put

00:06:58.560 --> 00:07:00.350
your hands to will

00:07:00.360 --> 00:07:02.550
prosper. So if you've got to put your hand

00:07:02.560 --> 00:07:04.550
to something, you don't sit by with

00:07:04.560 --> 00:07:06.629
your thumb in your nose. You've got to go

00:07:06.639 --> 00:07:10.230
out and do something. Put your

00:07:10.240 --> 00:07:13.350
faith in action. Faith without works is

00:07:13.360 --> 00:07:15.749
dead. Now I sit there and go, 'Well, I'm

00:07:15.759 --> 00:07:17.350
just waiting. I want my angel to bring

00:07:17.360 --> 00:07:19.510
my sack of money.'I told you that's a

00:07:19.520 --> 00:07:21.830
miracle and that happens, but it's

00:07:21.840 --> 00:07:23.990
not something that happens all the time.

00:07:24.000 --> 00:07:26.550
I'd say more than what I've

00:07:26.560 --> 00:07:28.189
ever seen in my life, God says,

00:07:28.199 --> 00:07:31.670
'Brandon, go out and get it, buddy. Take

00:07:31.680 --> 00:07:34.390
your hand to it and make it happen. But

00:07:34.400 --> 00:07:36.670
I will bless whatever you put your hands

00:07:36.670 --> 00:07:36.680
to.'Do

00:07:36.680 --> 00:07:40.309
something with your life.

00:07:40.309 --> 00:07:40.319
You're

00:07:40.319 --> 00:07:42.390
waiting so much for the ice

00:07:42.400 --> 00:07:44.710
cream truck to come by,

00:07:44.720 --> 00:07:46.150
but you've got to go

00:07:46.160 --> 00:07:47.670
out and get it.

00:07:47.680 --> 00:07:49.749
Go down to Blue Bell

00:07:49.759 --> 00:07:51.230
and get you

00:07:51.240 --> 00:07:53.510
some.

00:07:54.720 --> 00:07:56.950
I haven't had ice cream in a while;

00:07:56.960 --> 00:07:58.070
the Lord won't let me have it. So, I'm

00:07:58.080 --> 00:08:00.510
thinking about it right

00:08:00.520 --> 00:08:04.749
now. It's like, 'Oh, God, help

00:08:04.749 --> 00:08:04.759
me.'Just

00:08:04.759 --> 00:08:07.430
being real. I was thinking

00:08:07.440 --> 00:08:09.950
about my ice

00:08:09.960 --> 00:08:13.029
cream, but we're getting over that.

00:08:13.039 --> 00:08:14.189
Anyway,

00:08:14.199 --> 00:08:18.950
doing these videos... okay.

00:08:18.960 --> 00:08:22.230
So, when we see the ground and you're

00:08:22.230 --> 00:08:22.240
sowing

00:08:22.240 --> 00:08:24.550
into the ground, look at the

00:08:24.560 --> 00:08:27.350
fruit that the ground has. What's going

00:08:27.360 --> 00:08:28.869
on around their ministry? Is their

00:08:28.879 --> 00:08:32.269
ministry prospering? Is their ministry

00:08:32.279 --> 00:08:35.589
flourishing? Has God anointed them? If

00:08:35.599 --> 00:08:38.149
you see change and souls are coming

00:08:38.159 --> 00:08:40.790
in like Billy Graham, you know Billy

00:08:40.800 --> 00:08:42.949
Graham was good soil, right? He's not

00:08:42.959 --> 00:08:44.470
here anymore, so I can use him as an example.

00:08:44.480 --> 00:08:46.870
You won't throw eggs at me.

00:08:46.880 --> 00:08:49.430
Billy Graham's soil—I'm sure at that

00:08:49.440 --> 00:08:51.670
time, I never sowed into

00:08:51.670 --> 00:08:51.680
it—was

00:08:51.680 --> 00:08:54.070
probably very fertile ground because

00:08:54.080 --> 00:08:56.870
why? He was getting a lot of people born

00:08:56.880 --> 00:09:00.150
again and his ministry was exploding.

00:09:00.160 --> 00:09:02.310
It was like, "Wow, look at what's going

00:09:02.320 --> 00:09:04.710
on with Billy Graham. Everybody knew

00:09:04.720 --> 00:09:06.389
Billy Graham."He was a household name,

00:09:06.399 --> 00:09:08.710
right? So,

00:09:08.720 --> 00:09:11.190
if you see somebody and God is really

00:09:11.200 --> 00:09:16.710
touching them, try it.

00:09:16.720 --> 00:09:19.110
That's all I can say. Try it. And maybe,

00:09:19.120 --> 00:09:21.750
just maybe,

00:09:21.760 --> 00:09:23.350
if you keep your heart right and

00:09:23.360 --> 00:09:25.389
don't badmouth them, you sit there and

00:09:25.389 --> 00:09:25.399
think,

00:09:25.399 --> 00:09:27.990
"God, you're obviously touching this

00:09:28.000 --> 00:09:30.870
individual for a reason. Something's

00:09:30.880 --> 00:09:31.949
going on with

00:09:31.959 --> 00:09:34.870
it. I'm going to test the

00:09:34.870 --> 00:09:34.880
ground."Now,

00:09:34.880 --> 00:09:36.949
if you have some of these

00:09:36.959 --> 00:09:39.269
others whose ground is their

00:09:39.279 --> 00:09:41.350
ministry, they're the same.

00:09:41.360 --> 00:09:43.750
Their following hasn't changed. If it seems

00:09:43.760 --> 00:09:47.710
that everything around them is

00:09:47.720 --> 00:09:51.389
dying, then you have to

00:09:51.399 --> 00:09:53.150
go.

00:09:53.160 --> 00:09:55.590
There's nothing wrong with

00:09:55.600 --> 00:09:58.710
small churches, but if the church is not

00:09:58.720 --> 00:10:01.910
getting any growth, if it is

00:10:01.920 --> 00:10:04.550
not bringing anybody to get saved, if

00:10:04.550 --> 00:10:04.560
it's

00:10:04.560 --> 00:10:06.949
not baptizing, if

00:10:06.949 --> 00:10:06.959
it's

00:10:06.959 --> 00:10:08.630
not laying hands on the sick, if

00:10:08.630 --> 00:10:08.640
it's

00:10:08.640 --> 00:10:11.590
not casting out devils, I would

00:10:11.600 --> 00:10:13.710
consider why I'm going to church

00:10:13.720 --> 00:10:17.110
there. Does that make sense? You have to

00:10:17.120 --> 00:10:19.350
be careful where you're going. Don't go

00:10:19.360 --> 00:10:21.150
and put yourself in a church that's

00:10:21.160 --> 00:10:23.509
dead. They're not getting any outreach.

00:10:23.519 --> 00:10:25.110
They're not getting anybody saved.

00:10:25.120 --> 00:10:26.470
They're just there

00:10:26.480 --> 00:10:27.990
on a Sunday

00:10:27.990 --> 00:10:28.000
or

00:10:28.000 --> 00:10:29.350
Wednesday. They have a couple Bible

00:10:29.360 --> 00:10:31.110
studies and go home, and they're not

00:10:31.120 --> 00:10:34.710
really into expanding our tent and

00:10:34.710 --> 00:10:34.720
reaching

00:10:34.720 --> 00:10:38.910
the nations for

00:10:38.920 --> 00:10:40.949
Jesus because that's what we're there

00:10:40.959 --> 00:10:43.509
for anyway. I don't want to just have

00:10:43.519 --> 00:10:46.150
a feel-good sermon.

00:10:46.160 --> 00:10:48.310
Maybe have a potluck; some people

00:10:48.320 --> 00:10:49.829
have potlucks, you know, they'll

00:10:49.839 --> 00:10:52.069
have some tables or have some

00:10:52.079 --> 00:10:54.230
fried chicken or

00:10:54.240 --> 00:10:55.910
whatever, and they'll eat and have a

00:10:55.920 --> 00:10:58.069
little fellowship. And

00:10:58.079 --> 00:11:00.150
you

00:11:00.160 --> 00:11:02.949
walk away and think, "But did we get

00:11:02.959 --> 00:11:04.910
anybody new

00:11:04.920 --> 00:11:10.990
saved? Did we try? Did we help

00:11:10.990 --> 00:11:11.000
anybody?"Year

00:11:11.000 --> 00:11:14.990
after year, it's

00:11:14.990 --> 00:11:15.000
the

00:11:15.000 --> 00:11:19.110
same old thing. But if you're

00:11:19.120 --> 00:11:21.910
trying to expand your borders and you're

00:11:21.920 --> 00:11:25.190
letting the Holy Ghost flow, and you see

00:11:25.200 --> 00:11:27.750
people's lives

00:11:27.750 --> 00:11:27.760
changing—drug

00:11:27.760 --> 00:11:31.190
addicts or prostitutes or

00:11:31.190 --> 00:11:31.200
whatever—and

00:11:31.200 --> 00:11:33.230
they're getting their lives set

00:11:33.240 --> 00:11:36.670
free, then by all means, man, that's

00:11:36.680 --> 00:11:40.069
alive. I want to be where it's alive. I

00:11:40.079 --> 00:11:42.790
want to see people's lives changed from

00:11:42.800 --> 00:11:46.069
glory to glory where the Holy

00:11:46.079 --> 00:11:49.350
Ghost is allowed to move. It happens. There

00:11:49.350 --> 00:11:49.360
are

00:11:49.360 --> 00:11:51.350
churches

00:11:51.360 --> 00:11:53.509
like that. Collinsville is one.

00:11:53.519 --> 00:11:54.870
Pastor

00:11:54.880 --> 00:11:57.269
Candace and Chip let

00:11:57.279 --> 00:11:59.750
the Holy Ghost move, but there

00:11:59.750 --> 00:11:59.760
are

00:11:59.760 --> 00:12:02.550
some folks that won't.

00:12:02.560 --> 00:12:05.190
I'm trying to paint a

00:12:05.200 --> 00:12:07.269
picture that it's not all the soil's

00:12:07.279 --> 00:12:10.949
fault. You've got to call in your seed,

00:12:10.959 --> 00:12:13.030
you've got to water your seed, and

00:12:13.040 --> 00:12:14.790
you've got to be speaking. Don't be

00:12:14.800 --> 00:12:17.190
speaking double. A double-minded man is

00:12:17.200 --> 00:12:19.590
unstable in all his ways. You can't be

00:12:19.600 --> 00:12:21.190
saying, "Well,

00:12:21.200 --> 00:12:23.509
we're broke, busted, and

00:12:23.509 --> 00:12:23.519
disgusted.

00:12:23.519 --> 00:12:25.829
We're never going to get anything. We're

00:12:25.839 --> 00:12:27.750
always going to be poor. Grandma was

00:12:27.760 --> 00:12:30.870
poor, we're poor, and my

00:12:30.880 --> 00:12:34.949
kids are going to be poor."No,

00:12:34.949 --> 00:12:34.959
we are

00:12:34.959 --> 00:12:37.030
barrier breakers.

00:12:37.040 --> 00:12:40.550
Poverty

00:12:40.560 --> 00:12:43.190
stops with us. We're not having it ever

00:12:43.200 --> 00:12:44.870
again. We're not going to live in it. I

00:12:44.870 --> 00:12:44.880
am

00:12:44.880 --> 00:12:46.949
going to decree and declare that

00:12:46.959 --> 00:12:49.430
the blessing and the favor of God is on

00:12:49.440 --> 00:12:51.590
me, and that everything I put my hands

00:12:51.600 --> 00:12:54.870
to will prosper. Everything I do,

00:12:54.880 --> 00:12:56.949
Father, I'm anointed to do it, and

00:12:56.959 --> 00:12:59.110
you've appointed me for such a time as

00:12:59.120 --> 00:13:01.750
this. My angels are going out right

00:13:01.760 --> 00:13:03.670
now from the north, south, east,

00:13:03.670 --> 00:13:03.680
and

00:13:03.680 --> 00:13:07.069
west, and bringing my harvest

00:13:07.079 --> 00:13:09.430
in. I thank you, Holy Spirit, that

00:13:09.440 --> 00:13:11.590
you're bringing favor.

00:13:11.600 --> 00:13:14.069
Everywhere I go, I have favor. When

00:13:14.079 --> 00:13:16.310
I walk into a store, I have favor.

00:13:16.320 --> 00:13:18.150
Whenever I walk out of the store, I have

00:13:18.160 --> 00:13:20.230
favor because I'm blessed coming in, I'm

00:13:20.240 --> 00:13:22.150
blessed going out, I'm blessed in the

00:13:22.160 --> 00:13:24.310
city, and I'm blessed in the field. You've

00:13:24.320 --> 00:13:26.550
got to believe it, but you've got to say it

00:13:26.560 --> 00:13:28.389
out of your mouth. Stop that

00:13:28.389 --> 00:13:28.399
milly-mouthed

00:13:28.399 --> 00:13:30.870
talking.

00:13:39.120 --> 00:13:42.069
Life and death is in the power of your

00:13:42.079 --> 00:13:44.550
tongue and you're eating the fruit of

00:13:44.560 --> 00:13:45.870
what you've been

00:13:45.880 --> 00:13:47.990
saying. Remember that, ladies and

00:13:48.000 --> 00:13:49.829
gentlemen.

00:13:53.519 --> 00:13:55.509
As a man thinketh in

00:13:55.519 --> 00:13:59.350
his heart, so is he. The Bible says as a

00:13:59.360 --> 00:14:01.990
man thinketh in his heart, so is he. So

00:14:01.990 --> 00:14:02.000
don't

00:14:02.000 --> 00:14:04.389
take thoughts that contradict what

00:14:04.399 --> 00:14:05.829
you feel in your heart.

00:14:12.399 --> 00:14:14.150
Out of the

00:14:14.160 --> 00:14:16.189
abundance of the heart, the mouth

00:14:16.199 --> 00:14:18.870
speaks.

00:14:21.360 --> 00:14:23.189
The more you say it, the more you're

00:14:23.199 --> 00:14:25.750
going to reap it. And you have more

00:14:25.760 --> 00:14:27.910
power over your seed than just the bad

00:14:27.920 --> 00:14:29.430
ground is what the Holy Spirit said to

00:14:29.440 --> 00:14:32.069
me. You need to know that. He said,

00:14:32.079 --> 00:14:33.590
"Brenda, you can't just blame that on

00:14:33.600 --> 00:14:36.230
the preacher's ground."He said,

00:14:36.240 --> 00:14:37.990
"There's a lot of them that

00:14:38.000 --> 00:14:39.590
are out there saying out of their

00:14:39.600 --> 00:14:42.949
mouth, 'Well, I never get a

00:14:42.959 --> 00:14:44.870
harvest.'"You

00:14:44.880 --> 00:14:46.550
need to learn, because I've

00:14:46.560 --> 00:14:48.470
learned

00:14:52.639 --> 00:14:55.509
to watch my words.

00:14:55.519 --> 00:14:57.990
I've never, since I've

00:14:58.000 --> 00:15:01.030
been raising my son in the last 16

00:15:01.040 --> 00:15:05.110
years, said poverty out

00:15:05.120 --> 00:15:09.110
of my mouth. We

00:15:15.360 --> 00:15:18.389
refuse to live by

00:15:18.399 --> 00:15:20.470
the curse of the law. I'm blessed

00:15:20.480 --> 00:15:22.949
because Deuteronomy 28 says

00:15:22.949 --> 00:15:22.959
so.

00:15:22.959 --> 00:15:26.629
I believe that Isaac planted in

00:15:26.639 --> 00:15:28.949
famine and reaped a hundredfold that same

00:15:28.959 --> 00:15:31.829
year. I believe that God is no

00:15:31.829 --> 00:15:31.839
respecter

00:15:31.839 --> 00:15:34.150
of persons and that what he did for

00:15:34.160 --> 00:15:38.590
Isaac, he'll do for me. Isaac

00:15:38.590 --> 00:15:38.600
sowed

00:15:38.600 --> 00:15:43.269
in famine. Genesis 26,

00:15:43.279 --> 00:15:46.870
one of my favorite chapters.

00:15:46.880 --> 00:15:49.069
Isaac sowed in

00:15:49.079 --> 00:15:52.230
famine, and that same year he reaped a

00:15:52.230 --> 00:15:52.240
hundredfold.

00:15:52.240 --> 00:15:54.470
So he sowed in famine.

00:15:54.480 --> 00:15:56.629
There was no rain, but God still

00:15:56.639 --> 00:15:59.269
blessed it.

00:15:59.279 --> 00:16:01.110
It's not all just about the soil;

00:16:01.120 --> 00:16:03.590
it's what you

00:16:03.600 --> 00:16:06.389
believe and what you say out of your mouth.

00:16:06.399 --> 00:16:08.870
Life and death is in

00:16:08.880 --> 00:16:11.110
the power of your tongue. So you have

00:16:11.120 --> 00:16:13.350
to take authority over your words.

00:16:13.360 --> 00:16:15.910
You need to take communion and call crop

00:16:15.920 --> 00:16:19.110
failure over every bad word you've said,

00:16:19.120 --> 00:16:22.069
over every idle word of poverty, lack,

00:16:22.079 --> 00:16:25.189
and milly-mouthed talk like, "Oh,

00:16:25.199 --> 00:16:26.629
we're never going to get out of this

00:16:29.519 --> 00:16:31.670
house."I

00:16:36.560 --> 00:16:38.870
always have the blessing on my life.

00:16:38.880 --> 00:16:41.509
Why? Because I believe in

00:16:41.519 --> 00:16:44.150
the covenant that God has given me.

00:16:44.160 --> 00:16:46.470
Greater is he that is in me than he that

00:16:46.480 --> 00:16:48.550
is in the world. And he's given me the

00:16:48.560 --> 00:16:50.870
ability and the power to get wealth with

00:16:50.880 --> 00:16:53.829
these hands. Show me, Holy Spirit, how

00:16:53.839 --> 00:16:56.710
to do it today.

00:16:56.720 --> 00:16:58.949
Give me wisdom on where I'm

00:16:58.959 --> 00:17:02.150
supposed to put my boat into

00:17:02.160 --> 00:17:05.710
motion. Faith without works is

00:17:05.720 --> 00:17:08.710
dead. And if you're not doing something

00:17:08.720 --> 00:17:11.189
to bring it forth,

00:17:11.199 --> 00:17:13.750
your faith is not working. You

00:17:13.750 --> 00:17:13.760
are snared

00:17:13.760 --> 00:17:15.110
by the words of your

00:17:15.120 --> 00:17:18.789
mouth, too. So it all

00:17:18.799 --> 00:17:21.270
works like that big motor;

00:17:21.280 --> 00:17:23.510
it all ticks together. And if you're

00:17:23.520 --> 00:17:25.029
not walking in love and you're walking

00:17:25.039 --> 00:17:26.390
in strife and you're doing all the

00:17:26.400 --> 00:17:27.909
things, you're

00:17:27.919 --> 00:17:29.909
putting a dam on the blessing coming

00:17:29.919 --> 00:17:32.070
into your household. And I always come

00:17:32.080 --> 00:17:34.470
before covenant with this communion

00:17:34.480 --> 00:17:35.990
all the time. That's why we have it

00:17:36.000 --> 00:17:37.830
everywhere. I got sacks of them

00:17:37.840 --> 00:17:40.070
everywhere because I believe in the

00:17:40.080 --> 00:17:42.549
power of the blood of Jesus. I believe

00:17:42.559 --> 00:17:44.710
in the power of the communion and what

00:17:44.720 --> 00:17:47.430
he did for me. This is

00:17:47.440 --> 00:17:49.110
all about it right now, ladies and

00:17:49.120 --> 00:17:51.270
gentlemen: Palm Sunday going into the

00:17:51.280 --> 00:17:53.990
crucifixion of Good Friday and

00:17:54.000 --> 00:17:56.549
saying, "Jesus, thank you for what you

00:17:56.559 --> 00:17:59.350
did for me and you delivered me from

00:17:59.360 --> 00:18:02.150
Deuteronomy 28 according to your

00:18:02.150 --> 00:18:02.160
word."He

00:18:02.160 --> 00:18:04.710
said in Galatians, "Christ has

00:18:04.720 --> 00:18:07.750
redeemed me from the curse of the

00:18:07.750 --> 00:18:07.760
law."And

00:18:07.760 --> 00:18:09.590
this is what he'd redeemed me from:

00:18:09.600 --> 00:18:11.789
Deuteronomy 28 and all those curses

00:18:11.799 --> 00:18:14.870
down below it. He redeemed me

00:18:14.880 --> 00:18:17.110
from every single one of those curses.

00:18:17.120 --> 00:18:19.510
Deuteronomy 28 says all those blessings

00:18:19.520 --> 00:18:21.990
will come upon those,

00:18:21.990 --> 00:18:22.000
and

00:18:22.000 --> 00:18:23.990
he redeemed me from every one

00:18:24.000 --> 00:18:26.630
of them. I'm not underneath the curse

00:18:26.640 --> 00:18:29.590
because Galatians says that Christ

00:18:29.600 --> 00:18:31.990
redeemed me from all the curses of

00:18:32.000 --> 00:18:34.390
Deuteronomy 28, ladies and gentlemen.

00:18:34.400 --> 00:18:36.390
And we don't have to walk in sickness.

00:18:36.400 --> 00:18:38.630
We don't have to walk in lack. We can

00:18:38.640 --> 00:18:40.549
walk in abundance. And that's why we

00:18:40.559 --> 00:18:42.630
have to speak and decree a thing out of

00:18:42.640 --> 00:18:45.029
our mouth. Say it because life and death

00:18:45.039 --> 00:18:47.190
is in the power of your tongue. And

00:18:47.200 --> 00:18:49.430
faith calls those things that be not as

00:18:49.440 --> 00:18:51.270
though they were. And you have to speak

00:18:51.280 --> 00:18:53.510
it out your mouth. You have to say it

00:18:53.520 --> 00:18:56.470
out your mouth: "I believe. I receive a

00:18:56.470 --> 00:18:56.480
million-dollar

00:18:56.480 --> 00:18:58.110
check in the name of

00:18:58.110 --> 00:18:58.120
Jesus."Stretch

00:18:58.120 --> 00:19:01.430
out there big—that's big

00:19:01.440 --> 00:19:04.070
to me. I'm believing for a $100,000

00:19:04.080 --> 00:19:06.150
check. I believe. You say it out your

00:19:06.160 --> 00:19:07.669
mouth:

00:19:07.679 --> 00:19:10.870
"I believe for a $10,000 check."You may

00:19:10.880 --> 00:19:13.350
just be at a $500 level. That's fine. Or

00:19:13.360 --> 00:19:15.190
a $100 level. I believe for a $100

00:19:15.200 --> 00:19:18.070
check. Say it out your mouth. And the

00:19:18.080 --> 00:19:20.070
more you say it, the more you believe it

00:19:20.080 --> 00:19:21.510
because your heart's going to start to

00:19:21.520 --> 00:19:23.669
change. You're going to start to change.

00:19:23.679 --> 00:19:25.390
It's like dumping in clean water: when you see the

00:19:25.400 --> 00:19:28.230
oil and the dirty water, you keep dumping

00:19:28.240 --> 00:19:29.830
in the clean, clean, clean, and

00:19:29.840 --> 00:19:31.270
eventually it keeps filtering. It'll

00:19:31.280 --> 00:19:34.150
filter all that mess out of you. The

00:19:34.160 --> 00:19:37.190
more the life, the more this lifegiving

00:19:37.200 --> 00:19:39.750
beautiful Bible, this beautiful word

00:19:39.760 --> 00:19:42.310
gets on the inside of you and it becomes

00:19:42.320 --> 00:19:44.070
real to you. The more you get this

00:19:44.080 --> 00:19:46.470
inside of you and you go from glory to

00:19:46.480 --> 00:19:49.669
glory, that pouring water filters

00:19:49.679 --> 00:19:53.710
all that trash out because this is

00:19:53.720 --> 00:19:56.070
life. And so the more you get it, the

00:19:56.080 --> 00:19:57.430
more you won't think that because you're

00:19:57.440 --> 00:19:59.270
renewing your mind to the word of God.

00:19:59.280 --> 00:20:01.270
You got to renew your mind.

00:20:01.280 --> 00:20:03.029
You got to

00:20:03.039 --> 00:20:06.470
think what this word says about you. I

00:20:06.480 --> 00:20:09.990
believe what the Bible says about me. I

00:20:10.000 --> 00:20:12.549
can have what the Bible says I can have.

00:20:12.559 --> 00:20:14.710
Just like John Osteen used to say, "I

00:20:14.720 --> 00:20:16.230
believe what the word of God says about

00:20:16.240 --> 00:20:18.150
me. I can have what the Bible says I

00:20:18.150 --> 00:20:18.160
have."I'm

00:20:18.160 --> 00:20:20.549
not going to be moved by what

00:20:20.559 --> 00:20:22.630
I see. I'm not moved by what I feel. I'm

00:20:22.640 --> 00:20:24.150
going to be moved by what the word of

00:20:24.160 --> 00:20:26.549
God says. That's what you got to do. And

00:20:26.559 --> 00:20:27.909
that's what you got to believe. So,

00:20:27.919 --> 00:20:29.190
like I said, you can't just sit there

00:20:29.200 --> 00:20:31.110
and say, "Well, it's all about the

00:20:31.110 --> 00:20:31.120
preacher."No,

00:20:31.120 --> 00:20:33.590
it's about you, too.

00:20:33.600 --> 00:20:35.110
You got to say things out your mouth.

00:20:35.120 --> 00:20:37.510
That's right. Life and death

00:20:37.520 --> 00:20:39.990
is in the power of your tongue.

00:20:40.000 --> 00:20:43.430
Remember that. So, I don't know what got

00:20:43.440 --> 00:20:45.190
me off on that, but Holy Ghost, I guess,

00:20:45.200 --> 00:20:47.110
he wanted that to be said. He told

00:20:47.120 --> 00:20:48.789
me, he said, "Brandon, you're missing

00:20:48.799 --> 00:20:50.950
it. You got to say more than that. You

00:20:50.960 --> 00:20:53.190
got to say more than that, son. You got

00:20:53.200 --> 00:20:54.549
to say more than that. It's not just

00:20:54.559 --> 00:20:56.390
about planting in the good ground,

00:20:56.400 --> 00:20:58.390
but you got to water your

00:20:58.390 --> 00:20:58.400
seed."Just

00:20:58.400 --> 00:21:00.070
like a farmer, we got to believe for the

00:21:00.080 --> 00:21:01.750
rain. You got to believe for the rain

00:21:01.760 --> 00:21:03.029
and believe for fertilizer. You got to

00:21:03.039 --> 00:21:04.710
believe for all this stuff. We got to

00:21:04.720 --> 00:21:06.789
say it and then you got to believe it

00:21:06.799 --> 00:21:09.549
and then you receive it. Be

00:21:09.559 --> 00:21:12.430
discerning and look around

00:21:12.440 --> 00:21:15.830
you.

00:21:15.840 --> 00:21:17.830
What kind of fruit is happening? Whose

00:21:17.840 --> 00:21:20.149
lives are being changed? Because the

00:21:20.159 --> 00:21:22.950
Holy Spirit's in that. When you see

00:21:22.960 --> 00:21:25.430
people's lives being changed and they're

00:21:25.440 --> 00:21:27.909
not staying the same and you can look at

00:21:27.919 --> 00:21:29.510
them a year later and that

00:21:29.520 --> 00:21:31.190
baby Christian's getting the meat of the

00:21:31.200 --> 00:21:33.190
word and they're learning how to stand

00:21:33.200 --> 00:21:36.870
and have a backbone—my goodness,

00:21:36.880 --> 00:21:39.110
that has to be some good ground there.

00:21:39.120 --> 00:21:41.470
Does that make sense? Because if they're

00:21:41.480 --> 00:21:44.950
not, bottom line is, y'all, I want

00:21:44.960 --> 00:21:47.669
you to be blessed. I don't want you to

00:21:47.679 --> 00:21:50.390
struggle. I don't want you to live

00:21:50.400 --> 00:21:52.870
another day in poverty. I don't want you

00:21:52.880 --> 00:21:55.149
to live another day in sickness and

00:21:55.159 --> 00:21:57.590
disease. This is the most beautiful time

00:21:57.600 --> 00:22:00.310
of the year for you to

00:22:00.320 --> 00:22:04.470
have an

00:22:04.470 --> 00:22:04.480
inward-looking examination.

00:22:04.480 --> 00:22:07.669
Check yourself and say, "Where

00:22:07.679 --> 00:22:09.630
am I at right now with the

00:22:09.640 --> 00:22:11.990
Father? Where am I at with the blessing

00:22:12.000 --> 00:22:13.830
on my life? Where am I at with healing

00:22:13.840 --> 00:22:16.070
and not walking into disease

00:22:16.080 --> 00:22:17.990
and poverty and lack and not enough?

00:22:18.000 --> 00:22:21.950
Am I in

00:22:21.960 --> 00:22:24.390
overflow? Is there anything that I can

00:22:24.400 --> 00:22:28.149
do to increase in my life to change, to

00:22:28.159 --> 00:22:30.789
tweak some things?"Maybe just

00:22:30.799 --> 00:22:34.710
a little bit. No, nobody's perfect.

00:22:34.720 --> 00:22:36.630
None of us are. But I'm going to tell

00:22:36.640 --> 00:22:38.950
you, we all strive to be more like

00:22:38.960 --> 00:22:41.669
Jesus. It's all about looking at him and

00:22:41.679 --> 00:22:43.830
staying vertical and saying, "Jesus, I

00:22:43.840 --> 00:22:46.710
want to be more like you. I've got a

00:22:46.720 --> 00:22:49.990
long way to go, Father. But one day, I

00:22:50.000 --> 00:22:52.789
believe from going from glory to glory,

00:22:52.799 --> 00:22:56.549
I'm being more and more like you.

00:22:56.559 --> 00:22:59.549
Thank you, Lord. I receive it by

00:22:59.549 --> 00:22:59.559
grace."But

